get.description:
This operation allows you to retrieve a list of mandates (aka Direct Debits) along with the mandate ID
(`id`) to be able to retrieve a specific mandate later via `GET
/mandates/{mandateId}`.

It must be filtered by The Bank of London account ID (`accountId`) to
retrieve only mandates (aka Direct Debits) for a specific account. 

### Example request:

```
GET /mandates?accountId=GB-040075-12345678
```

The API will respond with an array of objects that contain all the details of the resulting mandates.

### Example response:
